ps://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/124318/', '', 'Asenapine, Pimavanserin, Ziprasidone, Lumateperone, Iloperidone, Amisulpride, Droperidol, Cariprazine, Brexpiprazole, Paliperidone, Lurasidone', 'Ciclesonide, Mometasone furoate, Budesonide, Flunisolide, Fluticasone, Cromoglicic acid, Betamethasone, Nedocromil, Triamcinolone, Beclomethasone dipropionate', 1767369485);
